TITLE: Configuring Per-Tenant Authentication in ASP.NET Core
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to set up per-tenant authentication in an ASP.NET Core application using Finbuckle.MultiTenant. It includes adding authentication services, configuring Finbuckle.MultiTenant services, and setting up the middleware.
