TITLE: Implementing EFCore Store Database Context
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a database context for the EFCore store by extending EFCoreStoreDbContext.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Finbuckle/Finbuckle.Website/blob/main/content/docs/v8.1.2/Stores.md#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
public class MultiTenantStoreDbContext : EFCoreStoreDbContext<TenantInfo>
{
  protected override void OnConfiguring(DbContextOptionsBuilder optionsBuilder)
  {
      // Use InMemory, but could be MsSql, Sqlite, MySql, etc...
      optionsBuilder.UseInMemoryDatabase("EfCoreStoreSampleConnectionString");
      base.OnConfiguring(optionsBuilder);
  }
}
```

